            "title": "盤中速報 - 富國銀行(WFC-US)大跌5.62%，報81.77美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>富國銀行(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:WFC:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/WFC\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">WFC-US</a>)截至台北時間14日21:33股價下跌4.87美元，報81.77美元，跌幅5.62%，成交量1,781,757（股），盤中最高價83.16美元、最低價81.20美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：+0.28%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：+0.45%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：+0.85%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+0.61%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>富國銀行(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:WFC:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/WFC\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">WFC-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：+5.85%</li> <li>近 1 月：+16.92%</li> <li>近 3 月：-7.4%</li> <li>近 6 月：+9.78%</li> <li>今年以來：-7.04%</li></ul></section></main>",
